&lt;p&gt;This is not a native iOS or Android role. The role is focused on web-first product experiences, APIs, and platform integrations that can be reused across mobile web and native app surfaces; to help us scale features across platforms and create compelling features that deepen reader engagement and increase user retention.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
